ion, even if we can’t run it.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a dedicated test for the active dynamic-access class:\n\n- Added `tests/src/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-test-autoconfigure/2.7.18/src/test/java/org_springframework_boot/spring_boot_test_autoconfigure/TypeExcludeFiltersContextCustomizerTest.java`\n\nThe new test drives Spring’s public `TestContextManager` API with `@TypeExcludeFilters`, exercising both supported `TypeExcludeFilter` constructor paths:\n\n- `Class<?>` constructor path:\n  - `Class#getDeclaredConstructor(Class[])`\n  - `Constructor#newInstance(Object[])`\n- no-argument constructor fallback path:\n  - fallback `Class#getDeclaredConstructor(Class[])`\n  - no-arg `Constructor#newInstance(Object[])`\n\nI did not run compilation or tests, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_066334cca5c73096016a0360ffcb708190a1f7c2f70e8fdb94\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1208, "output": 681, "cacheRead": 17920, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 19809, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1778606320635, "responseId": "resp_066334cca5c73096016a0360f1b3a48190a9379793756e5b83"}, "toolResults": []}
